      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Missed revenue today (last 24h)",
      "description": "Measured shortfall: (`baseline_atc_per_hour` \u00d7 24h) \u2212 today's actual cart-adds, valued at `avg_atc_value`. Positive = revenue left on the table due to outages, slowdowns, or capacity caps. Negative = you over-performed baseline.",
