    {
      "id": 207,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "\ud83d\uded1 Projected outage cost \u2014 what a future N-hour outage would cost",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 1,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 21
      },
      "collapsed": false,
      "panels": []
    },
    {
      "id": 208,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "transparent": true,
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 8,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 22
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "code": {
          "language": "plaintext",
          "showLineNumbers": false,
          "showMiniMap": false
        },
        "content": "### How we calculate\n\n**Loss rate ($/hour)** = `Baseline ATC / hour` \u00d7 `Avg cart-add value`\n**Outage cost** = `Loss rate` \u00d7 `Outage duration`\n**Annual exposure** = `Loss rate` \u00d7 `1% \u00d7 8 760` (= 87.6 hr/yr)\n\n> Tune the four variables at the top of the page to drive the numbers live.\n> Default baseline (`360 / hr`) \u2248 the p75 of a healthy week.\n> Even a 99 % uptime SLA still bleeds **87 hours / yr** at the loss rate shown."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 209,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Cost of this outage",
      "description": "What a `${outage_hours}` hour outage at baseline rate costs you in cart-add revenue.",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 8,
        "x": 8,
        "y": 22
      },
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${datasource_prom}"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "${datasource_prom}"
          },
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "${baseline_atc_per_hour} * ${avg_atc_value} * ${outage_hours}",
          "legendFormat": "",
          "range": true
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "currencyUSD",
          "decimals": 0,
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "#F472B6",
                "value": null
